Package: simrasch
Title: Implements functions to simulate performance of item infit statistics used in Rasch modeling
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Fabian", "Dablander", email = "dostodabsi@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Peter", "Edelsbrunner", email = "peter.edelsbrunner@ifv.gess.ethz.ch", role = c("aut")))
Description: Accompanying R package to a talk given at ECPA13. Implements simulations scrutinizing item infit statistics in Rasch modeling. Also includes presentation slides.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.1)
